'''夏洛特·埃玛·艾奇逊'''（{{Lang-en|Charlotte Emma Aitchison}}，{{bd|1992年|8月2日|carIdx=Aitchison, Charlotte}}），艺名'''查莉·XCX'''（英語：{{Lang|en|Charli XCX}}），是一名英国[[歌手|歌手]]和[[詞曲作家|詞曲作家]]，出生于[[英国|英国]][[剑桥|剑桥]]。

查莉于2008年发布了自己的第一支独立单曲，并在[[伦敦|伦敦]]的仓库舞会首次表演。她於2010年與{{Le|庇护所唱片|Asylum Records}}簽約，并發佈了首張[[混音带|混音带]]《{{Lang|en|Heartbreaks and Earthquakes}}》。查莉的第二張混音带《{{Lang|en|Super Ultra}}》於2012年發佈。在2013年，查莉推出首張專輯《{{le|真實浪漫史|True Romance (Charli XCX album)}}》，包括單曲{{单双书号转换|{{le|You (Ha Ha Ha)}}}}和{{单双书号转换|{{le|Nuclear Seasons}}}}。

在2013和2014年期間，查莉憑藉與[[Icona_Pop|Icona Pop]]合作的單曲{{单双书号转换|[[I_Love_It_(Icona_Pop歌曲)|I Love It]]}}及與[[伊基·阿塞莉娅|伊基·阿塞莉娅]]合作的單曲{{单双书号转换|Fancy}}在國際上著名。{{单双书号转换|[[怦怦心跳_(酷娃恰莉歌曲)|怦怦心跳]]}}於2014年發布，是同年上映電影《[[生命中的美好缺憾_(電影)|生命中的美好缺憾]]》的主題曲，歌曲在各國音樂排行榜取得了前十名的好成績。同年查莉發佈了專輯《{{le|爛咖|Sucker (album)}}》，這張專輯包括了{{单双书号转换|[[打破它_(酷娃恰莉歌曲)|打破它]]}}、{{单双书号转换|Doing It}}等歌曲。

== 早期生活 ==
查莉於1992年8月2日出生于[[英国|英国]][[剑桥|剑桥]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://search.findmypast.co.uk/results/world-records/england-and-wales-births-1837-2006?firstname=charlotte%20emma%20&lastname=aitchison|title=Results for England & Wales Births 1837-2006|publisher=SDearch.findmypast.co.uk|accessdate=2014-12-18|archive-date=2015-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705005425/http://search.findmypast.co.uk/results/world-records/england-and-wales-births-1837-2006?firstname=charlotte%20emma%20&lastname=aitchison|dead-url=no}}</ref>，父亲是[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]人，母亲是印度人，来自乌干达。她在[[赫特福德郡|赫特福德郡]]长大。<ref name="4music">{{cite episode|title=This Week's Fresh Music Top 20|publisher=[[4Music|4Music]]|airdate=15 April 2014}}</ref>查莉在14歲時就開始創作了。<ref name="interview">{{cite web |last=Needham |first=Alex |url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/music/brit-pop-girls |title=Brit Pop Girls |work=[[Interview_(magazine)|Interview]] |date=2009-07-27 |accessdate=2013-04-18 |archive-date=2013-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928175835/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/music/brit-pop-girls |dead-url=no }}</ref>之後她進入了[[畢曉普斯托福德|畢曉普斯托福德]]大學，並於2010年離開。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/The.Old.Stortfordian.Society|title=A post from 2 July 2013 on the Old Stortfordian Society's Facebook page|author=|date=|work=Facebook|accessdate=2014-10-12|archive-date=2016-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160501122055/https://www.facebook.com/The.Old.Stortfordian.Society|dead-url=no}}</ref> 隨後進入[[伦敦大学学院|伦敦大学学院]]攻读美术学位，一年后退学。<ref name=SMH>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/music/quirky-charli-xcx-has-worked-hard-to-earn-her-spot-in-the-limelight-20150420-1mork8.html|title=Quirky Charli XCX has worked hard to earn her spot in the limelight|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|access-date=2015-05-03|archive-date=2016-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927090251/http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/music/quirky-charli-xcx-has-worked-hard-to-earn-her-spot-in-the-limelight-20150420-1mork8.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 職業生涯 ==
===2008–12: 早期表演与录制===
在14岁时，查莉开始使用她父母的贷款录制她的首张专辑。在 2008 年年初，她开始在[[Myspace|Myspace]]页面上上传这张专辑的歌曲和其他的Demo。这引起了许多非法仓库舞会和伦敦东部派对的注意，并邀请她来表演。<ref name="mm">{{cite web|url=http://www.moustachemagazine.com/2012/10/interview-with-charli-xcx/|title=Interview with Charli XCX|author=|date=|publisher=|accessdate=2014-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325232819/http://www.moustachemagazine.com/2012/10/interview-with-charli-xcx/|archive-date=2016-03-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Chris Tinkham |url=http://www.undertheradarmag.com/interviews/charli_xcx/ |title=Charli XCX - This Is Me |publisher=Under the Radar |date=2013-09-12 |accessdate=2014-11-18 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929202722/http://www.undertheradarmag.com/interviews/charli_xcx |dead-url=no }}</ref>她的艺名「Charli XCX」是她年轻时她[[MSN_Messenger|MSN Messenger]]的屏幕名称。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sJeQa1KDrU|title=Charli XCX explains "XCX" - On Air with Ryan Seacrest|work=YouTube|accessdate=2014-12-18|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307034306/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sJeQa1KDrU|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管她的演出是非法的，她的父母仍然支持她追求她的事业，并与她参加晚会。<ref name=Darkstar>{{cite web|last1=Nika|first1=Colleen|title=Dark Star Rising: Charli XCX Talks Rave Roots and Her Colorful Future|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/blogs/thread-count/dark-star-rising-charli-xcx-talks-rave-roots-and-her-colorful-future-20120322|website=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2014-07-21|archive-date=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130614205115/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/blogs/thread-count/dark-star-rising-charli-xcx-talks-rave-roots-and-her-colorful-future-20120322|dead-url=yes}}</ref>她于2008年底发布了[[单曲|单曲]]{{单双书号转换|!Franchesckaar!}}和雙A面单曲{{单双书号转换|Emelline/Art Bitch}}。首张专辑《14》并没有商业发行，只有少量的促销拷贝和用于赠送的副本。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.complex.com/music/2013/03/interview-charli-xcx-talks-debut-album-internet-haters-icona-pop |title=Interview: Charli XCX Talks Debut Album, Internet Haters, and Writing Icona Pop's "I Love It" |publisher=Complex |date= |accessdate=2013-04-18 |archive-date=2014-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122121926/http://www.complex.com/music/2013/03/interview-charli-xcx-talks-debut-album-internet-haters-icona-pop |dead-url=no }}</ref>在 2010 年与 {{tsl|en|Asylum Records|Asylum 唱片}}签约之后，她休息了一段时间，并自称为“迷失时期”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/nov/30/charli-xcx-true-romance|title=Charli XCX - Guardian Interview|author=|date=|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2014-10-12|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917214536/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/nov/30/charli-xcx-true-romance|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年5月，查莉发行了单曲{{单双书号转换|Stay Away}}，随后于 11 月发行{{单双书号转换|Nuclear Seasons}}。两支[[单曲|单曲]]均由{{le|阿雷爾·雷徹夏德|Ariel Rechtshaid}}制作并仅在英国发行。它们吸引了音乐网站[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]的注意，并将它们列入2011年最佳歌曲排行榜。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/features/staff-lists/8726-the-top-100-tracks-of-2011/7/|title=Pitchfork - The Best Songs of 2011|author=|date=|work=Pitchfork|accessdate=2014-10-12|archive-date=2016-02-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229075357/http://pitchfork.com/features/staff-lists/8726-the-top-100-tracks-of-2011/7/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012 年 5 月，查莉发布了首个[[混音带|混音带]]《{{Lang|en|Heartbreaks and Earthquakes}}》，其中一个音轨由八首歌曲组成。同年，她支持了Santigold和[[酷玩乐队|酷玩乐队]]的巡演。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/rita-ora/news/coldplay-support-act/| title = Rita Ora On Coldplay Support Slots: "It's Such A Huge Opportunity" - Audio| accessdate = 2012-05-29| date = 2012-05-09| publisher = [[Capital_(radio_network)|Capital FM]]| archive-date = 2021-01-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210116125556/https://www.capitalfm.com/artists/rita-ora/news/coldplay-support-act/| dead-url = no}}</ref>第二张原创混音带《{{Lang|en|Super Ultra}}》于11月在她的网站上发行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/news/48504-download-charli-xcxs-super-ultra-mixtape/|title=Charli XCX - Super Ultra|author=|date=|work=Pitchfork|accessdate=2014-10-12|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201214920/https://pitchfork.com/news/48504-download-charli-xcxs-super-ultra-mixtape/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 2012–13: 《真实浪漫史》 ===
[[File:Charli_XCX_@_Postivus_2013_(9819955206).jpg|thumb]]
查莉曾与[[瑞典|瑞典]]流行音乐组合[[Icona_Pop|Icona Pop]]共同编写并献声2012年的单曲{{单双书号转换|[[I_Love_It_(Icona_Pop歌曲)|I Love It]]}}。2013年1月，这首歌出现在电视剧《[[女孩我最大|女孩我最大]]》之后，<ref name="billboard">{{cite web |last=Lipshutz |first=Jason |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5740380/charli-xcx-previews-second-album-with-superlove-single-watch-video |title=Charli XCX Previews Second Album with 'SuperLove' Single: Watch Video |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]] |date=2013-09-26 |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924121515/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5740380/charli-xcx-previews-second-album-with-superlove-single-watch-video |dead-url=no }}</ref>这首歌进入了[[美国|美国]][[公告牌百强单曲榜|《公告牌》百强单曲榜]]，并获得了第7名的最好成绩。<ref name="billboard-peak">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1560133/pink-holds-at-no-1-on-hot-100-while-rihanna-rules-at-radio|title=Pink Holds at No. 1 on Hot 100 While Rihanna Rules at Radio|last=Trust|first=Gary|accessdate=2013-05-02|archive-date=2014-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108161345/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1560133/pink-holds-at-no-1-on-hot-100-while-rihanna-rules-at-radio|dead-url=no}}</ref>它也曾获得[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]的冠军。

查莉的第二张录音室专辑《{{le|真實浪漫史|True Romance (Charli XCX album)}}》在2013年4月发行。紧随其后的是单曲{{单双书号转换|You're the One}}和{{单双书号转换|You (Ha Ha Ha)}}。她曾说：“这张专辑的每一部分都源自于我自己的浪漫历史，它是非常纯粹的，非常真诚的，也是非常真实的。”<ref name="announce">{{cite web |last=Snapes |first=Laura |url=http://pitchfork.com/news/49703-charli-xcx-announces-debut-album-true-romance/ |title=Charli XCX Announces Debut Album, ''True Romance'' |publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]] |date=2013-02-26 |accessdate=2013-03-02 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126082727/http://pitchfork.com/news/49703-charli-xcx-announces-debut-album-true-romance/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>这张专辑在[[英国专辑排行榜|英国专辑排行榜]]上获得了最高 85名的成绩。<ref name="ukchrats">{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/albums-chart/ |title=Official UK Albums Top 100 |publisher=[[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]] |date=2013-04-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GCHzd4yF?url=http://www.officialcharts.com/albums-chart/ |archivedate=2013-04-27 |accessdate=2013-04-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在告示牌每周唱片排行榜中最高成绩第5名，在[[澳大利亚唱片业协会榜|澳大利亚唱片业协会榜]]中最高成绩第11名。<ref name="heat seekers">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-05-04/heatseekers-albums |title=Heatseekers Albums : May 04, 2013 | Billboard Chart Archive |publisher=Billboard.com |date=2013-05-04 |accessdate=2013-05-21 |archive-date=2014-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420194707/http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-05-04/heatseekers-albums |dead-url=no }}</ref>《真实浪漫史》廣受樂評好评。在评论彙總网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，《真实浪漫史》根據18份評論獲得76/100的评价。<ref name="MC">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/true-romance/charli-xcx/critic-reviews |title=True Romance – Charli XCX |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]. [[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2013-04-21 |archive-date=2013-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419021006/http://www.metacritic.com/music/true-romance/charli-xcx/critic-reviews |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 2013-15: 《爛咖》 ===

2013年6月，查莉开始致力于她的第三张专辑。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1567371/charli-xcx-already-writing-new-music-for-second-album?utm_source=twitter|title=Charli XCX Already Writing Music for Second Album|author=|date=2013-06-19|work=Billboard|accessdate=2014-10-12|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924130233/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1567371/charli-xcx-already-writing-new-music-for-second-album?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月，她发布了单曲{{单双书号转换|SuperLove}}。这是她独立进入[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]的第一支单曲，并取得了 62名的成绩。<ref name=UKSingleChart>{{cite web|title=CHARLI XCX - UK Singles Chart|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/Charli%20XCX|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=2014-08-26|archive-date=2014-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016145313/http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/charli%20xcx/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2014年2月，她客串了澳洲饒舌歌手[[伊姬·阿潔莉亞|伊姬·阿潔莉亞]]的单曲{{单双书号转换|Fancy}}。<ref name="popdust">{{cite web |author=Jacques Peterson |url=http://popdust.com/2014/02/06/listen-to-iggy-azalea-and-charli-xcxs-cocky-new-single-fancy/ |title=Listen To Iggy Azalea and Charli XCX's Cocky New Single, 'Fancy' |publisher=Popdust |date=2012-09-29 |accessdate=2014-04-13 |archive-date=2014-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409030136/http://popdust.com/2014/02/06/listen-to-iggy-azalea-and-charli-xcxs-cocky-new-single-fancy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>这支单曲曾登顶[[美国|美国]][[公告牌百强单曲榜|《公告牌》百强单曲榜]]，成为两人的首支冠军单曲。<ref name="yahoomusic">{{cite web|url=https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/chart-watch-meet-iggy-azalea-211310608.html|title=Chart Watch: Meet Iggy Azalea|publisher=YAHOO|date=2014-05-29|accessdate=2014-05-29|archive-date=2014-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529053120/https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/chart-watch-meet-iggy-azalea-211310608.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Sam Lansky |url=http://time.com/12334/iggy-azalea-fancy-clueless-charli-xcx-video/ |title=Iggy Azalea and Charli XCX's Homage to Clueless Will Have You Totally Buggin' |publisher=TIME |date=2014-03-04 |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2014-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420120040/http://time.com/12334/iggy-azalea-fancy-clueless-charli-xcx-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

