單曲《Vroom Vroom》原本是用於預告第3張錄音室專輯即將發行的宣傳曲。<ref>{{Cite news|first=Michael|last=Cragg|url=http://www.thebeatjuice.com/2017/03/17/hit-machine-read-interview-charli-xcx-paris-hilton/|title=The Hit Machine: Read an Interview with Charli XCX|magazine=[[The_Beat_(magazine)|The Beat]]|date=2017-03-17|access-date=2017-03-17|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Postal_Service|Metropolitan Postal Service]]|location=London, England|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318085803/http://www.thebeatjuice.com/2017/03/17/hit-machine-read-interview-charli-xcx-paris-hilton/|archive-date=2017-03-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 作為一張{{Le|先鋒流行|Avant-pop}}<ref name="rs11">{{cite web | url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/live-reviews/charli-xcx-explores-new-avant-pop-direction-with-sophie-at-sxsw-20160319 | title=Charli XCX Explores New Avant-Pop Direction with Sophie at SXSW | publisher=Rolling Stone | date=2016-03-19 | accessdate=2016-10-14 | author=Knopper, Steve | archive-date=2016-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820150951/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/live-reviews/charli-xcx-explores-new-avant-pop-direction-with-sophie-at-sxsw-20160319 | dead-url=no }}</ref> 的迷你專輯，跟前期的專輯比恰莉在風格上出現急遽的變化，並獲得了褒貶不一的評論。同名單曲的音樂影片於2016年4月發布至[[Apple_Music|Apple Music]]。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.spin.com/2016/04/charli-xcx-vroom-vroom-music-video-watch-sophie/ | title=Charli XCX's Video Is Sleek, Sensational, and Star-Making | work=Spin | date=2016-04-22 | accessdate=2016-04-22 | author=Carley, Brennan | archive-date=2016-04-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425040926/http://www.spin.com/2016/04/charli-xcx-vroom-vroom-music-video-watch-sophie/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

