萊爾·科特里爾|克萊羅]]、和{{le|Yaeji}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://charli-the-album.co.uk/|title=Charli xcx|website=Charli xcx|language=en|access-date=2019-06-13|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613190021/https://www.charli-the-album.co.uk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

