iews/charlie-xcx-how-im-feeling-now-album-review-lockdown-a9515111.html|title=Charli XCX review, How I'm Feeling Now: A brash, adventurous lockdown album|website=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=2020-05-15|accessdate=2020-05-15|archive-date=2020-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518103729/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/charlie-xcx-how-im-feeling-now-album-review-lockdown-a9515111.html|url-status=live}}</ref> According to [[Metacritic|Metacritic]], the album currently ties with ''[[Pop_2_(mixtape)|Pop 2]]'' as Charli XCX’s most acclaimed project to date,<ref>{{Cite web|title=Charli XCX|url=https://www.metacritic.com/person/charli-xcx|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|language=en|access-date=2020-05-18|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520040143/https://www.metacritic.com/person/charli-xcx|url-status=live}}</ref> with [[Kitty_Empire|Kitty Empire]] of ''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]'' describing it as "a work of its time."<ref>{{Cite news|last=Empire|first=Kitty|date=2020-05-16|title=Charli XCX: How I'm Feeling Now review – truly a work of its time|language=en-GB|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2020/may/16/charli-xcx-how-im-feeling-now-review-show-and-tell-turned-up-to-11|access-date=2020-05-18|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518135604/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2020/may/16/charli-xcx-how-im-feeling-now-review-show-and-tell-turned-up-to-11|url-status=live}}</ref>
