|website=Undertheradarmag.com|accessdate=2016-06-28|archive-date=2016-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160731130008/http://www.undertheradarmag.com/news/charli_xcx_reschedules_north_american_tour_dates/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 和[[另類搖滾|另類流行]]。<ref>{{cite web|first=Duncan|last=Cooper|url=http://www.thefader.com/2016/08/16/charli-xcx-cover-story-interview|title=How Charli XCX Stopped Worrying And Learned To Love The Pop Machine|magazine=[[The_Fader|The Fader]]|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2017-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171024131932/http://www.thefader.com/2016/08/16/charli-xcx-cover-story-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她早期的作品被形容是{{Le|暗潮|Dark wave}}和{{Le|女巫浩室|Witch house (genre)}}的混和體。 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pitchfork.com/features/rising/8734-charli-xcx/|title=Charli XCX|website=[[Pitchfork_(website)|Pitchfork]]|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123083014/https://pitchfork.com/features/rising/8734-charli-xcx/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在自己的事業逐漸步入正軌後，她更是在自己的首張專輯中使用了[[歌德搖滾|歌德流行]]和[[合成器流行|合成器流行]]等多種曲風，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.list.co.uk/article/51546-charli-xcx-true-romance/|title=Charli XCX – True Romance|date=2013-06-10|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2017-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819190859/https://www.list.co.uk/article/51546-charli-xcx-true-romance/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/dec/27/the-playlist-the-best-pop-of-2014-charli-xcx-taylor-swift|title=The playlist: the best pop of 2014, with Charli XCX and Taylor Swift|first=Michael|last=Cragg|date=2014-12-27|accessdate=2017-10-26|via=The Guardian|archive-date=2017-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819192407/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/dec/27/the-playlist-the-best-pop-of-2014-charli-xcx-taylor-swift|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她的第2張專輯被媒體稱作融合了[[龐克搖滾|龐克搖滾]]、[[新浪潮|新浪潮]]和[[強力流行|強力流行]]元素的[[流行龐克|流行龐克]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/charli-xcx-sucker-20141217|title=Charli XCX 'Sucker' Album Review|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010130835/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/charli-xcx-sucker-20141217|dead-url=no}}</ref>.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://consequenceofsound.net/2014/12/album-review-charli-xcx-sucker/|title=Album Review: Charli XCX – Sucker|date=2014-12-22|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2017-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929132554/https://consequenceofsound.net/2014/12/album-review-charli-xcx-sucker/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/cdreviews/11422212/Charli-XCX-Sucker-review-high-impact-pop.html|title=Charli XCX, Sucker, review: 'high-impact pop'|first=Neil|last=McCormick|date=2015-02-21|accessdate=2017-10-26|via=The Daily Telegraph|archive-date=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824172440/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/cdreviews/11422212/Charli-XCX-Sucker-review-high-impact-pop.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/20066-sucker/|title=Charli XCX: Sucker Album Review|website=Pitchfork|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2021-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329040559/https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/20066-sucker/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2016後，她最新的作品《[[Vroom_Vroom|Vroom Vroom]]》開始朝{{Le|先鋒流行|Avant-pop}}的風格發展，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/live-reviews/charli-xcx-explores-new-avant-pop-direction-with-sophie-at-sxsw-20160319|title=Charli XCX Explores New Avant-Pop Direction at SXSW|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820150951/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/live-reviews/charli-xcx-explores-new-avant-pop-direction-with-sophie-at-sxsw-20160319|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rollingstone.com"/> 並同時融合了[[歐陸舞曲|歐陸舞曲]]的元素，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/reviews/albums/charli-xcx-vroom-vroom|title=Charli XCX's new EP is a nihilist rebellion from someone who's never known 'pop' as a dirty word|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2017-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819192817/https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/reviews/albums/charli-xcx-vroom-vroom|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而隔年發行的混音帶《[[第1名天使|Number 1 Angel]]》同樣展現出了受[[陷阱音樂|陷阱樂]]、[[當代節奏藍調|節奏藍調]]、[[電音流行|電音流行]]、[[合成器流行|合成器流行]]和{{Le|實驗流行|Experimental pop}}等多種曲風影響的多元風格。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/allsongs/2017/03/10/519644995/charli-xcxs-mixtape-number-1-angel-is-a-fantastic-pop-diary|title=Charli XCX's Mixtape 'Number 1 Angel' Is A Fantastic Pop Diary|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010033432/http://www.npr.org/sections/allsongs/2017/03/10/519644995/charli-xcxs-mixtape-number-1-angel-is-a-fantastic-pop-diary|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rollingstone.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/review-charli-xcxs-number-1-angel-mixtape-w472136|title=Review: Charli XCX Commits to Avant-Pop Partnership on 'Number 1 Angel'|accessdate=2017-10-26|archive-date=2017-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929153650/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/review-charli-xcxs-number-1-angel-mixtape-w472136|dead-url=no}}</ref> 大眾媒體時常以她去和[[關·史蒂芬妮|關·史蒂芬妮]]<ref>[http://www.vh1/.com/news/5641/modern-singers-who-sound-like-classic-artists/] {{dead link|date=June 2016}}</ref> 和[[瑪琳娜·戴曼迪斯|瑪琳娜]]等歌手的聲線作比較。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stereogum.com/1339022/marina-and-the-diamonds-charli-xcx-just-desserts/mp3s/|title=Marina and the Diamonds & Charli XCX – "Just Desserts"|last=Nelson|first=Michael|date=2013-05-01|website=Stereogum|accessdate=2016-06-28|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930104126/https://www.stereogum.com/1339022/marina-and-the-diamonds-charli-xcx-just-desserts/mp3s/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

