酷娃恰莉有色彩[[聯覺|聯覺]]。她曾說：「我看到的音樂是彩色的。我喜歡黑色、粉色、紫色或者是紅色的音樂——但我不喜歡綠色、黃色或者是棕色的音樂。」<ref>{{cite web |first=Mark |last=Savage |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-25330600 |title=Charli XCX: Pop, punk and synaesthesia |date=2013-12-11 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2015-01-06 |archive-date=2015-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214172459/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-25330600 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 她認為自己是[[女性主義|女權主義者]]並寫下歌曲《Body of My Own》作為立場宣言。<ref>{{cite web |first=Ryan |last=Smith |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3022942/Charli-XCX-unveils-feminist-track-self-pleasure.html |title='Girls should own their bodies': Charli XCX unveils 'feminist' track about self pleasure... as she admits to feeling like a pop 'outsider' |date=2015-04-02 |work=Daily Mail |accessdate=2015-05-27 |archive-date=2019-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190919125304/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3022942/Charli-XCX-unveils-feminist-track-self-pleasure.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 她同時也製作了有關性別平等的2015年的紀錄片《The F Word and Me》，該片於[[英國廣播公司第三台|英國廣播公司第三台]]首次上映。<ref>{{cite web |first=Daniel |last=Kreps |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/watch-charli-xcxs-feminism-film-the-f-word-and-me-20151125 |title=Watch Charli XCX's Feminism Film 'The F Word and Me' |date=2015-11-25 |work=Rolling Stone |access-date=2019-08-17 |archive-date=2017-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227095646/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/watch-charli-xcxs-feminism-film-the-f-word-and-me-20151125 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

酷娃恰莉把自己活動的時間主要劃分成倫敦、[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，跟加州等3個地區。<ref>{{cite interview|title=Charli XCX in Studio|date=1 February 2017|accessdate=9 February 2018|interviewer=KiddNation|last=XCX|first=Charlie|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_dOg1lxvP4|publisher=YouTube|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326060115/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_dOg1lxvP4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

